{"per_page":10,"total":7,"current":1,"data":[{"title":"使用TensorRT加速PyTorch模型","date":"2021-04-16T13:55:20.000Z","excerpt":"<p>本文将介绍使用TensorRT推理引擎对PyTorch模型进行加速，便于算法的部署。</p>","link":"speed-up-pytorch-model-using-tensorrt","tags":["pytorch","tensorrt"],"categories":["machine-learning"]},{"title":"强连通分量","date":"2021-01-05T11:52:50.000Z","thumbnail":"strongly-connected-component/logo.png","excerpt":"<p>本文描述强连通分量的概念及使用深度优先搜索将有向图分解为强连通分量的方法。</p>","link":"strongly-connected-component","tags":["SCC"],"categories":["algorithm"]},{"title":"MPI基础","date":"2020-05-17T14:09:54.000Z","thumbnail":"mpi/mpi_logo.jpg","excerpt":"<p>MPI(Message Passing Interface)是消息传递函数库的标准规范，有着多种实现，如MPICH、OPEN-MPI等。本文以MPICH为例介绍MPI的基本使用。</p>","link":"mpi","tags":["mpi","multiprocessing"],"categories":["tools"]},{"title":"大数据量下均值和方差的增量计算","date":"2020-05-13T22:25:28.000Z","excerpt":"<p>本文介绍如何在大数据量下增量计算均值和方差。</p>","link":"big-data-mean-std","tags":["big-data","math"],"categories":["algorithm"]},{"title":"计算机视觉-几何变换","date":"2020-04-08T13:07:17.000Z","thumbnail":"computer-vision-geometric-transformation/geometric.png","excerpt":"<p>本文介绍几何变换(Geometric Transformation)的相关知识，包括：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>齐次坐标</li>\n<li>线性变换<ul>\n<li>欧几里得变换</li>\n<li>仿射变换</li>\n<li>射影变换</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>坐标系统</li>\n</ol>","link":"computer-vision-geometric-transformation","tags":["computer-vision"],"categories":["machine-learning"]},{"title":"OpenMP基础","date":"2020-04-08T10:04:28.000Z","thumbnail":"openmp-basic/openmp.png","excerpt":"<p>本文介绍 OpenMP C++版本的基本使用方法。</p>","link":"openmp-basic","tags":["multiprocessing"],"categories":["programming-language"]},{"title":"[论文笔记] Focal Loss for Region Proposal Network","date":"2020-04-04T15:37:13.000Z","excerpt":"<p><img src=\"focal-loss-for-region-proposal-network/1585988538880.png\" alt=\"1585988538880\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>类别不均衡的问题不止存在于one-stage检测器中，two-stage检测器面临着同样的问题，鉴于focal loss在one-stage上的成功应用，作者将focal loss应用于RPN，检验 focal loss 在two-stage检测器中的作用。</p>","link":"focal-loss-for-region-proposal-network","tags":["loss","object-detection","rpn"],"categories":["paper-note"]},{"title":"[论文笔记] Focal Loss for Dense Object Detection","date":"2020-04-03T22:36:07.000Z","excerpt":"<p>作者提出了 Focal Loss 损失函数，在交叉熵损失的基础上加入因子 <svg xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"8.932ex\" height=\"2.843ex\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.838ex;\" viewbox=\"0 -863.1 3845.9 1223.9\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-labelledby=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\n<title id=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">(1 - p_t)^\\gamma</title>\n<defs aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-28\" d=\"M94 250Q94 319 104 381T127 488T164 576T202 643T244 695T277 729T302 750H315H319Q333 750 333 741Q333 738 316 720T275 667T226 581T184 443T167 250T184 58T225 -81T274 -167T316 -220T333 -241Q333 -250 318 -250H315H302L274 -226Q180 -141 137 -14T94 250Z\"/>\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-31\" d=\"M213 578L200 573Q186 568 160 563T102 556H83V602H102Q149 604 189 617T245 641T273 663Q275 666 285 666Q294 666 302 660V361L303 61Q310 54 315 52T339 48T401 46H427V0H416Q395 3 257 3Q121 3 100 0H88V46H114Q136 46 152 46T177 47T193 50T201 52T207 57T213 61V578Z\"/>\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-2212\" d=\"M84 237T84 250T98 270H679Q694 262 694 250T679 230H98Q84 237 84 250Z\"/>\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMATHI-70\" d=\"M23 287Q24 290 25 295T30 317T40 348T55 381T75 411T101 433T134 442Q209 442 230 378L240 387Q302 442 358 442Q423 442 460 395T497 281Q497 173 421 82T249 -10Q227 -10 210 -4Q199 1 187 11T168 28L161 36Q160 35 139 -51T118 -138Q118 -144 126 -145T163 -148H188Q194 -155 194 -157T191 -175Q188 -187 185 -190T172 -194Q170 -194 161 -194T127 -193T65 -192Q-5 -192 -24 -194H-32Q-39 -187 -39 -183Q-37 -156 -26 -148H-6Q28 -147 33 -136Q36 -130 94 103T155 350Q156 355 156 364Q156 405 131 405Q109 405 94 377T71 316T59 280Q57 278 43 278H29Q23 284 23 287ZM178 102Q200 26 252 26Q282 26 310 49T356 107Q374 141 392 215T411 325V331Q411 405 350 405Q339